    - assign from inventory, stop, pause, delete DONE
    - better debugging capabilities DEFERRED
  - Some sort of graphical state machine editor
    - editor for llscripts DONE
    - generic editor DEFERRED
  - Maybe direct support for editing logic using blender bricks DEFERRED
  - Doors, pickables, physics DONE
  - Maybe support for running in game engine mode
    - control of avatar DONE
    - synchronize all object positions DONE

